  fb:m.0d05w3 fb:location.country.official_language ?language .
  ?language rdfs:label ?label
  FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?year WHERE {
  fb:m.0713r fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?date .
  BIND( YEAR( ?date ) AS ?year )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?year )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?senator ?label WHERE {
  ?pos fb:government.government_position_held.jurisdiction_of_office fb:m.04ly1 ; fb:government.government_position_held.office_position_or_title ?title .
  ?pos fb:government.government_position_held.office_holder ?senator .
  ?senator rdfs:label ?label
  FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = 'en' ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?title ) , 'state senator' ) )
}
